name: Portræt af en bydel
summary_text: Poul Martinsen takes on a ride with night doctors on the streets in Vesterbro's slum area where bronchitis and inflammation of the middle ear have become chronic diseases.

name: Portræt af Svend Heinild
summary_text: Gyda Uldall interviews the Danish doctor Svend Heinild.

name: Pati Patni
summary_text: Gauri marries Amar who later meets with an accident. She becomes the sole breadwinner of the family and he starts suspecting her of having an affair.

name: Ostatatzi
summary_text: Ivan enters Annie's apartment with the intention of stealing everything he can. Chained to the crime scene, he excuses himself for being a friend of her husband. This is followed by infidelity, which will lead to despair and suicide.

name: The Naked Man
summary_text: The heir to £500,000 must live for one month without assistance.

name: Myeongdongi teuldae
summary_text: The fighters of the Korean Indpendence Army struggle against the colonial policies of Japan in the early 1900's.

name: Min musik - din musik
summary_text: Jørgen de Mylius interviews Keld Heick and his daughter Annette Heick. The two Heicks tell about themselves and what kind of music they each prefer.

name: Majeok
summary_text: A Japanese commander promises to release the Korean prisoners of war if the Korean Independence Army manages to rescue the daughter of a British diplomat who was kidnapped by bandits.

name: Maengho jakjeon
summary_text: Under the command of Lt Choi, the Tiger Squad, fighting the Viet Cong during the Vietnam War, uncover a beautiful but deadly spy with vital strategic information.

name: Louis Jouvet ou L'amour du théâtre
Kinova - demir yumruk
summary_text: A Turkish adaptation of the famous Italian western comic book series, Kinowa.
